<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>

    <p>Hello <%=User.find_by_id(@request.user).name%>! Your request to tutor someone in the course <%= Course.find_by_id(@request.course).name%> in <%=@request.location%> has been accepted! In your request, you said you wanted to tutor in the following topics: <%= @request.topics%> </p>
    <p>
      It is now your turn to reach out to the person who has accepted your request, <%= @user.name%>, at their email, which is <%= @user.email%>. Don't forget to request a rating for the session and some feedback when you two are done!
    </p>
    <p>Have fun and happy teaching! If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
    <p>Best, <br> TeachMe</p>
  </body>
</html>